\n兩個人相處得舒服開心就好<br />\n順其自然啦絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:14:54.000Z","msg":"條女好撚自9私又唔識自我反省"},{"pid":"eb35ad30b6c58c2826594575c6a0d5c81467a9bc","tid":1871092,"uid":150852,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c28f9dfb6f8e7ea9344f73b0e0b455a46b5b932","tid":1871092,"uid":301839,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"21dbd193af69d48973235b28613c5f4bc9cf79d1","tid":1871092,"uid":150852,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:13:43.000Z","msg":"你唔鍾意佢食<br />\n所以你想佢為你介<br />\n佢鍾意食<br />\n點解你唔可以為咗佢而接受<br />\n<br />\n其實雙向嘅啫冇得話邊個啱<br />\n只係你未夠動力令佢戒煙<br />\n一方面可以話佢唔體諒你<br />\n另一方面你都要問自己點解冇能力令佢為咗你戒<br />\n<br />\n感情嘅嘢好難去衡量<br />\n兩個人相處得舒服開心就好<br />\n順其自然啦絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:14:54.000Z","msg":"條女好撚自9私又唔識自我反省"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:16:19.000Z","msg":"仆街認真覆完先發覺佢成日開9post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4cd4a6a313630e9ee229a24a2a21fcf6fb0f30","tid":1871092,"uid":189506,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"希望樓主男朋友睇到呢個post<br />\n你睇下你條女幾撚麻煩，食支煙都響度呼天搶地，管住曬仲煩過自己老母，飛撚左條女去啦"},{"pid":"c3230acd2b3f01734507d4ae6d17cf2bc53c1786","tid":1871092,"uid":324671,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T09:21:49.000Z","msg":"屌你老母壓力咁撚大食隻煙都唔撚得"},{"pid":"e35375614c63e16a323b2eb4abaa27a2877f2f73","tid":1871092,"uid":242164,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T10:40:27.000Z","msg":"分手囉 好簡單   搵件唔食煙既     完"},{"pid":"7a1b5531e8ac12c6512e58256013a8b5d7759e02","tid":1871092,"uid":139487,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:33:30.000Z","msg":"I know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我男朋友食左好多年煙好難戒煙...但自己又好憎人食煙...又好愛佢勁矛盾..."},{"pid":"726a2bb0425a88c5d67e9caedb